    "created_at": "2025-08-07T18:15:04Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-08-07T18:15:04Z",
    "body": "Starship uses a library that is baked-in to interface with git, not a binary. Thus the interfaces works very differently.\n\nThis proposal in particular, a shell-based solution for detection, is also likely to run into performance issues as custom modules do in some cases.\n\nFurthermore, changing how all the git modules work is a larger undertaking that may not be worth the added maintenance burden.",
